      <!-- ── Terms acceptance ── -->
      <div class="hire-fieldset">
        <span class="hire-fieldset-legend">Terms acceptance</span>
        <p class="understand-intro">
          Tick each statement to confirm your understanding before submitting.
        </p>
        <div class="understand-list">

          <label class="understand-item">
            <input class="hire-check" type="checkbox" name="accept_payments" value="yes" required />
            <div class="understand-text">
              <strong>Progress payments</strong>
              I understand that progress claims must be paid within 7 Business Days of submission.
              Mackay Refrigeration may suspend work if payment is not received by the due date,
              and interest will accrue on all overdue amounts.
              <span class="clause-ref">Clauses 8.4, 8.5, 8.6</span>
            </div>
          </label>

          <label class="understand-item">
            <input class="hire-check" type="checkbox" name="accept_variations" value="yes" required />
            <div class="understand-text">
              <strong>Variations and price adjustments</strong>
              I understand that any variation to the Works must be agreed in writing and signed by
              both parties. If Equipment costs increase after the Contract is formed, or if I cause
              delays to the Works, the Price will be adjusted accordingly and I will be liable for
              any extra costs incurred by Mackay Refrigeration.
              <span class="clause-ref">Clauses 5, 9.1, 10.1, 13.2</span>
            </div>
          </label>

          <label class="understand-item">
            <input class="hire-check" type="checkbox" name="accept_cancellation" value="yes" required />
            <div class="understand-text">
              <strong>Cancellation and postponement</strong>
              I understand that if I postpone or cancel any Works or any part thereof, I must
              reimburse Mackay Refrigeration for all costs and expenses incurred in preparation,
              and may also be liable to pay Mackay Refrigeration's lost profit on the Works.
              <span class="clause-ref">Clause 9.2</span>
            </div>
          </label>

          <label class="understand-item">
            <input class="hire-check" type="checkbox" name="accept_ownership" value="yes" required />
            <div class="understand-text">
              <strong>Equipment ownership and risk</strong>
              I understand that Equipment remains the property of Mackay Refrigeration until the
              full Price and all other amounts owing are paid. Until then, I am a bailee of the
              Equipment and must not create any security interest in, or transfer possession of,
              the Equipment to any third party without written consent.
              <span class="clause-ref">Clauses 12.7, 12.8, 12.9, 20.10</span>
            </div>
          </label>

          <label class="understand-item">
            <input class="hire-check" type="checkbox" name="accept_liability" value="yes" required />
            <div class="understand-text">
              <strong>Limitation of liability</strong>
              I understand that Mackay Refrigeration's liability under this Agreement is limited to
              replacement or repair of Equipment or re-supply of services. Mackay Refrigeration is
              not liable for any consequential loss, loss of profits, loss of opportunity, or loss
              of use of the Site.
              <span class="clause-ref">Clauses 16.1, 16.2</span>
            </div>
          </label>

          <label class="understand-item">
            <input class="hire-check" type="checkbox" name="accept_guarantee" value="yes" required />
            <div class="understand-text">
              <strong>Personal guarantee</strong>
              I/We acknowledge that by executing this Agreement as Guarantor, I/we personally and
              unconditionally guarantee all amounts owing and all obligations of the Customer under
              this Agreement. This guarantee is continuing and is not discharged by any variation,
              indulgence, release, or dealing by Mackay Refrigeration with the Customer.
              <span class="clause-ref">Clauses 19.1, 19.3, 19.4</span>
            </div>
          </label>

        </div>
